Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To rest quietly at the end of the week
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}requires working diligently on the other six days of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not even the God in Genesis is exempt from this law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}- Kirk H. Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Arashiyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you have many good things that you can't lose in against Tatsuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Trust me, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No good!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My head just decided on its own to remember Mr. Moriaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And it also manipulated the memory rather conveniently!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my well earned Sunday!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I shouldn't think about school or teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll concentrate on this novel today and finish reading it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What you're holding is a chikuwa stuffed with mustard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You wouldn't normally confuse that sort of thing with dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the only one who could be the perpetrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did the main character have to have the teacher's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sis! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sis is occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lies. You were just zoning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Adults also treat zoning out as work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright. You're a good girl so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}play with your brother, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takeru, play with Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, there's something you can play together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something that beeps and bloops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do it please.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What... are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't get to save!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's your fault!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.93,0:03:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotori! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Augh, enough, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't today your day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you go out of your way to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something terrible happened to me at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanada might visit, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanada?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So Tatsuno is at that age...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Compared to her, Hotori is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyways Tatsuno, hear me out -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Recently, when I think about the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}this part of me feels funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh really, Hotori too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know. Whenever I think about math tests, my stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah no, I don't mean my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, things like differentials and integrals are beyond reason, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}... 7-11?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Differentials and integrals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can talk about difficult things, but I won't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I was in elementary school, I stumbled on dividing fractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I flip the top and bottom... will that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It still makes me uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And you've managed to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tatsuno isn't very good at listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Though it's very Hotori like to not realize
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the topic switched from love to math.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's said that people who handle dividing fractions easily
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}will also handle their lives easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} I've also seen that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you can't follow logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}if you're the type that can make conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then your life will move forward smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are formulas for life, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And now we've moved to theories of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leaving logic aside, if you can make conversation well, you'll be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can figure out the perpetrator in anime detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}if you follow a formula, even if you can't reason it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?! How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The character voiced by the best paid voice actor is the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Augh. Now I'll always know who the perp is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I shouldn't have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotori, if you're free, why don't you go to the grocery store and buy some potatoes and onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But... I'm a customer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then pay for your meal and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tsk. I'll go then.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lend me that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that goes vroom vroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}♬〜Potatoes and onions, potatoes and onions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}♬〜Potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, that was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it, jeez?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? You stopped me for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seeing dangerous people like that make me think it's Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}YOU'RE THE ONE WHO'S DANGEROUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't hit you that hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Women don't understand the seriousness of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's your fault for suddenly standing in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you before to not ride on the streets, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't knock it off I'm going to report this incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't ride on the streets?! Are you saying I should ride it in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My mom will get pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're putting the law below your mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you're a minor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen, ok? You have no license. You have no license plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have no headlights! You have no turn signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Due to the above reasons, you're not prepared to ride on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the same as a burger without the patty, cheese, lettuce, or pickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a depressing burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can I just eat the buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't stand this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine fine, I'll stop riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh. She's obedient today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cuz I've arrived already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Milk is best with bean jam bun, poko~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Running errands for the hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You got a problem with grandma, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have good carrots today! They've just been picked! Carrots! Freshly unearthed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's still mud stuck to them. Come get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be quiet! I'll forget what I came here to buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uhh... I feel like they were ingredients for curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah yeah, one of them was definitely potatoes and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potatoes and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Carrots please!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sure, thanks for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, Hotori,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The expiration date is tomorrow so drink it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If she drinks milk she might get a bit bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haha, ain't that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say will get bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We might have a sexual harassment case depending on your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try not to laugh with him.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.55,0:09:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to laugh, poko~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perverted old men. I'll remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't ride it. Push it home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Headlights and license plate, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And turn signal and license!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.78,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't simplify the problem. I'll confiscate your scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't handle this if I floor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, Tetsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tetsuno isn't... wait, I told you not to ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She'll go far away as a bride someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then it'll be as if the town has lost its fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But right now, it seems like she's starting fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanada really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's already back.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You mean she's late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cop said he was going to arrest me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Depressing burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good job. Have some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll just have a cup please. I'm having milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, so you'd like to get bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's too late for drinking milk to help now. You've already past your growth spurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you were to get a little smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it would be nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's just who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Arashiyama is Arashiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastard! You and everyone else! Just ignore my face and talk about my boobs, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to have a sexual harassment trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! Objection!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I was talking about your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! Sanada isn't that kind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Members of the audience may not speak without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be Sanada's attorney. Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Objection denied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like I was saying, height, not boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said potatoes and onions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.03,0:11:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anything you say can be used as evidence against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not a court, that's an arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forget the boobs, do something about her brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The popular name is "Sore Machi", poko~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world affairs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the maid greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why does "maid" get a Vulcan sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Vulcan one is like this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid is like this, turning into an M.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we make this our shop's greeting, we'll get more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What makes you say we'll get more?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mai... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1} I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Either way, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But if we aren't distinctive, customers won't come.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Meeting in session. No one may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Head maid! I found this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Customers don't come cuz you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world reflects one's own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the heart is peaceful, the world is filled with affection, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}when the heart is in pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the angry waves of adversity start to swirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's also an arrow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo. Aren't you the dry cleaning guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For some reason there are arrows posted around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh. I was actually walking around and following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this some sort of scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's grandma's place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh my. Some bad characters again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome hom...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.33,0:13:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An inconsistent shop, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma, what's with those arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What, arrows? Don't know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nyahaha.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I shall explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I spent two days around town putting up arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so customers would come following them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes ninja-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes shinobi-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're both the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hahaha, like that would make customers come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Might as well stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's have a meeting about the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah. We've already come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three cold waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}three cold waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}three coffees please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three katsu curries. Alright, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right here, don't play telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome hom...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.77,0:14:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These arrows...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neheheh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another person fell into my trap!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's rename this place "Café Antlion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So it was you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you peel them off for, you four eyed officer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Megapoli!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't just go and put these up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There were 30 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I worked so hard putting them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have to be my foe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't mean to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whenever I take action for the sake of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always run into you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're always getting in the way of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can say the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}our maid is an idiot. Here, have a cold one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chew on the ice and return to your den! Leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't stand this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't we tell you not to be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}rude to the customer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next time I don't know what'll happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a stupid fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoa, trying to imitate Beat Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bad impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Try saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! Tell me your names!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? So you spent over 30 minutes chasing middle schoolers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Head maid, what should we do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are no special considerations.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm cutting thirty minutes of pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why? I did it very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you seriously chase middle schoolers, catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean before that! The original greeting and the arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was for the sake of getting new customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}look at these never changing faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Do you have a complaint about your customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't we helping you out by eating katsu curry at such a weird hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't be able to eat dinner now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you giving this to me? I like eating with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Men with families are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I kinda understand what Arashiyama is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've been numbed to it recently but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the maid café's usual customers are all from the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like more guys to come who enjoy maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do the customers have to be pleasant to the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But Arashiyama's battle plan completely missed the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That greeting is especially terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha? Well at least we should make this place stand out more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's true. The sign looks like an impromptu thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about putting in an order for a new sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotori was a crybaby, as cute as a grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now she can talk about my management...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? What's the matter, Hotori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, have some curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't give him the chocolate after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm such a wimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, have some curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm crying cuz I lost my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, have some curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma?! What's with that outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What revolution is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid cafés seem profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C'mon, have some curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ate it, didn't ya Hotori. You ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have something to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since you've eaten curry free for the past 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you'll have to work here to pay it off your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotori was a crybaby, as cute as a grandchild...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I agree that we should do something about the sign
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to make our shop stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why don't we try something?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, there's a giant piece of cloth on the second floor, so
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}can you make me a showy banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Things have gotten interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You better take it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And there's also paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are we gonna write?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll write "Maid Café Seaside" really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you even know how to write the characters for café?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You talk big... but the results taper off like a tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The characters are like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Give me some paint. I'll write "Popular" in the empty space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Won't JARO complain?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.48,Default Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}(JARO - Japan Advertisement Review Organization)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be fine. We'll be popular after the sign goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice Tatsun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.89,Default Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fs46}Note: She just thought of a nickname for Tatsuno when she spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sauce katsudon in milk, poko~.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A bit over there. Pin it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Grandma, come look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We worked hard on it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Immature...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.47,0:20:07.18,Default Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Note: The ない next to the sign turns popular into immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That bastard dentist Naitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like no matter what I do today, the world gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world reflects one's own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the heart is peaceful, the world is filled with affection, but
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}when the heart is in pain, the angry waves of adversity start to swirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take this down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll cut this down and defeat the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Arashiyama, please do that sort of thing at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is what you need to be ninja and shinobi like for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean, ninja like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing to my sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I did a very immature thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you guys were to put on shows every day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you might get more customers, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, when you returned to the shop
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the victim was already collapsed here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suspect A: The beautiful owner of a boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suspect B: The taxi driver that drove her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Suspect C: The president of an IT company who invested in the boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The voice of the boutique owner is kinda cute and probably popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The poor looking taxi driver's voice actor has an austere voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The president definitely has a relationship with the boutique owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Err I mean, that voice seems popular too... it's a handsome voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's voiced by the best paid voice actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You couldn't possibly be suspecting Sachiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's the perp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He only played dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But he hasn't said anything yet. How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a rerun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom! Sis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotori! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Augh, enough, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now that I think about it, there's no year of the cat in the Chinese Zodiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's also no cat constellation in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why not? It's such a familiar animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Though there are cat mounds and cat promontories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have Tatsuno even though there are no dragons!
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.50,0:24:05.17,Default Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}(Tatsu = dragon)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you forget that I'm here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This smells like a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There must be a hidden truth behind why there's no cat year!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next time: Street number 3, Cat boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll be all over the place tomorrow, poko~
